== Active Time Battle ==

=== ATB Overview ===

The ATB system adds real-time elements to turn-based combat.

{| class="wikitable"
! Feature !! Description
|-
| ATB Gauge || Each character has a time bar
|-
| Fill Rate || Based on Agility stat
|-
| Action || Can act when gauge is full
|-
| Wait Mode || Game pauses in menus (optional)
|-
| Active Mode || Time flows continuously
|}

=== Gauge Mechanics ===

```
Fill Time = Base Time / (Agility + Equipment Bonuses)
Base Time = 65535 (frames at 60 fps)
```

