== Damage Calculations ==

=== Physical Damage ===

```
Base Damage = (Attack × 2) - Defense
Damage = Base × Multiplier × Random(0.875-1.125)
Multiplier = Level / 4 + Strength / 4

Minimum Damage = 1
Critical = Damage × 2
```

'''Attack Calculation:'''
```
Attack = Weapon Attack + Strength / 4 + Level / 4
```

=== Magical Damage ===

```
Base = Spell Power × (Intelligence / 2 + Level / 2)
Damage = Base × Elemental Modifier × Random(0.75-1.25)

Healing = Spell Power × Spirit / 4 + Level / 4
```

